  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Facilitate the workshop (Training)/seminar (Promote mental health & safety culture)</li><li>Perform general administrative duties (including procurement and logistics support)</li><li>Invoice processing</li><li>Update and maintain data records and database</li><li>Create and distribute company bulletins and communications</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirement</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Psychology (or in related field preferred)</li><li>Experience as workshop facilitator (MC), including coordination skills</li><li>3-4 years of experience in shipping industry is an added advantage</li><li>Excellent organizational skills with the ability to coordinate multiple\nstakeholders</li><li>Ability to communicate clearly, concisely,\nand politely</li><li>Proactive and self-motivated with strong problem-solving skills</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft\nOffice applications and experience with CANVA application is preferred</li><li>Strong oral and written communication skills in English</li></ul>",
