    "description": "<p>K MARINE SHIP MANAGEMENT PTE. LTD. has been established in Singapore, and the management of oil tankers, LPG carriers and LNG carriers will be transferred from “K” Line Energy Ship Management Co., Ltd. by the end of 2022.</p>\n<p>In addition, as one of the global bases that support the activities in Asia area of our business divisions from the forefront, we will accelerate efforts to decarbonize and introduce DX technology.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Find us here:</p>\n<p>https://kmsm.kline.com.sg/</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our company is a wholly owned subsidiary of Kawasaki Kisen Kaisha, Ltd, which is one of the most reputable and established Japanese shipping company having been established since 1919.</p>\n<p>Kawasaki Kisen Kaisha Ltd is also one of the biggest shipping groups in the world with interests in many shipping related businesses.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You can get to know more about the group here :</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>https://www.kline.co.jp/en/index.html</p>",
